skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: woodworker express
Developer Terms of Use
des:
This Skill provides the average person with an explanation of the many different terms they may come across when remodeling a kitchen or bathroom or building a project in their workshop. Ask Woodworker Express is a tool from WoodworkerExpress.com and works in conjunction with the woodworking terminology found on the website and elsewhere in everyday life. 

For customers of WoodworkerExpress.com, Ask Woodworker Express is also used to request order status and information for WoodworkerExpress.com orders. Lastly, the skill serves as a communication conduit to request a call back from Woodworker Express customer service.

Invoke the skill by saying, "Alexa, open Woodworker Express".

Then, simply ask questions by phrasing your questions to "Woodworker Express" such as
"Alexa, ask Woodworker Express what is a piano hinge?"
"Alexa, ask Woodworker Express what is the status of my order?"
"Alexa, ask Woodworker Express to request a call back from customer service"
"Alexa, ask Woodworker Express what is LED Lighting"
